const content = "<div id=\"mm-0\">\n    <section id=\"sObP6GwHMOZd_sObP6GwHMOZd\"><div><div><div id=\"\"><div><div><p>StatoilHydro</p></div></div></div><div><div><div><div><div id=\"\"><div><div><p></p><p>StatoilHydro is an international oil and gas company headquartered in Norway. StatoilHydro stock is traded on the NYSE under the symbol STO. Stat Oil Hydro has a 32.5% interest in the Marcellus Shale in partnership with Chesapeake Energy. This interest, managed from it's Houston office, covers more than 1.8 million acres in the Appalachian region of the United States including interests in Pennsylvania, West Virginia, New York, and Ohio. The company also has interests in fields in Canada, Mexico, Venezuela, Algeria, Libya, and Angola.</p><p><br></p><h2><strong>Contact Information for Royalty Owners - Tel. (713) 918-8200</strong></h2><p>Those who own gas royalties and mineral royalties are an important group to StatoilHydro. If you receive oil royalty or gas royalty from a lease under production by StatoilHydro, you can contact them at (713) 918-8200</p><p><br></p><h2><strong>StatoilHydro Production Volume Verification</strong></h2><p>If you are a lease holder (lessor) currently under production by StatoilHydro you can verify your oil and gas production volumes by visiting <a href=\"https://kennydubose.squarespace.com/owners-guide/leased-and-producing/oil-and-gas-production-volume-verification\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">How to Verify Your Oil and Gas Production Volumes</a>. This page includes links to the state agencies that record oil and gas production data and also covers the basics of how oil and gas is measured.</p><p></p></div></div></div></div></div><div><div><div id=\"\"><div><picture><source srcset=\"/images/statoilhydro.png, /images/statoilhydro.png\" media=\"(min-width: 992px)\"><source srcset=\"/images/statoilhydro.png, /images/statoilhydro.png\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\"><img srcset=\"/images/statoilhydro.png, /images/statoilhydro.png\" src=\"/images/statoilhydro.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" title=\"statoilhydro.png\" draggable=\"false\"></picture></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"\"><div><div data-brz-translate-text=\"1\"><p data-generated-css=\"brz-css-c1lJY\" data-uniq-id=\"f2pnu\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color2),1);\" href=\"/oil-gas-operators\" data-brz-link-type=\"page\">View All Oil &amp; Gas Operators</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></section>\n    <section id=\"5476867bb5c0d4e2e43a4df2533e422b_5476867bb5c0d4e2e43a4df2533e422b\"><div><div></div><div><div><div><div><div><div id=\"\"><div><picture><source srcset=\"/images/MineralWise-Logo-Transparent.png, /images/MineralWise-Logo-Transparent.png\" media=\"(min-width: 992px)\"><source srcset=\"/images/MineralWise-Logo-Transparent.png, /images/MineralWise-Logo-Transparent.png\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\"><img srcset=\"/images/MineralWise-Logo-Transparent.png, /images/MineralWise-Logo-Transparent.png\" src=\"/images/MineralWise-Logo-Transparent.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" title=\"MineralWise-Logo-Transparent.png\" draggable=\"false\"></picture></div></div></div></div><div><div><div id=\"\"><div><div data-brz-translate-text=\"1\"><p data-uniq-id=\"j0TjM\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-pjVpW\"><span style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color8),1);\">Use of this site constitutes acceptance of our </span><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color8),1);\" href=\"/terms-and-conditions\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\">Terms &amp; Conditions</a><span style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color8),1);\"> and </span><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color8),1);\" href=\"/privacy-policy\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\">Privacy Policy</a><span style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color8),1);\">.</span></p><p data-uniq-id=\"n27Va\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-sHEHX\"><em style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color8),1);\">© COPYRIGHT 2009-2025 KED INTERESTS, LLC - ALL RIGHTS RESERVED</em></p></div></d